- First read 2016 | 4 | Arm's length | Beautiful but kept at a distance
- Reread 2022 | 5 | Hit differently | Every passage about loss landed harder
- Museum of civilization | 5 | Destroyed me | This detail wrecked me on the second read
- Arthur Leander | 3 | Least favorite | Still my weakest thread but more earned now

